race.comment: BATTLE COMMANDER (2) is looking for the hat-trick today after a narrow victory over the mile at Ascot last time out. He technically drops back in grade today, but remains as the same weight as he returns to the midweeks. Hit his straps now and can continue his winning ways. GOLDEN DORE (3) ran on impressively first-up before being a little flat last time out when making the jump to Saturday company. He's third-up now and should be close to his top after just 1 trial coming into the campaign. Can put his best foot forward in what looks a very nice set up for him. MIA GUSTO (7) is another looking for the hat-trick following a good win in this grade last time out, reeling them in from the back of the pack. Pike replaces the apprentice hoop now in a big push for her chances. Watch for her flying late once again. FAME (1) creates some interest in his first run in WA. Keep safe. ATLANTIS BEACH (5) is not out of this on his best form and dropping back to the mile is a big tick.
